36	    it.todo("sword with enchantment 4 (year 0) returns 115 G (no high-ench surcharge)");
37	    it.todo("cursed sword with enchantment 5 (year 0) returns 195 G (100 + 50 curse + 30 high-ench + 10 first-ins + 5 fee)");
